<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/Tofu.png" type="image/png" />
    <title>藤原とうふ店 (自家用)</title>
</head>
<style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; 
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
                    "Noto Sans", Arial, sans-serif; }
        
    body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
           background-color: #f5f5f5; height: 100vh; padding: 20px; }

    .success-card { background: white; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center; }

    .icon-box { width: 80px; height: 80px; background: #4caf50; color: white;
            border-radius: 50%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            font-size: 40px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }

    h1 { font-size: 28px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 30px; }

    .back-btn { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #333; color: white;
            border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }

    .back-btn:hover { background: #555; transform: translateY(-2px); }
</style>
<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="icon-box">✓</div>
            <h1>訂單已收到！</h1>

        <button class="back-btn" onclick="location.href='/'">返回</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>